<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢٤٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1443">الْحَسَنُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5201">قُرَّةُ بْنُ حَبِيبٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3336">عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ دِينَارٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3644">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«مَا شَبِعْنَا حَتَّى فَتَحْنَا خَيْبَرَ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>